# Patterns of URLs lychee should skip during link checks.
# One regex per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.

# Internal UM platform, behind auth. Not reachable from CI.
^https://insight\.openclinica\.com/

# Repo's own deep links — checking them at push time creates noise
# when the script files are renamed in the same commit.
^https://github\.com/hihipy/sql-x-ray/

# Example links in code blocks (the dump's "generated_at" timestamp etc).
example\.com
